---
title: "US09 — Reset password"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>ForgotPasswordScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>RequestPasswordReset
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>User credentials (auth.users)
  A->>B: enter email, tap SEND RESET LINK
  B->>C: send(email)
  C->>E: sendPasswordResetEmail(email)
  E-->>C: ok (silent for unknown emails)
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (done)
  B-->>A: "reset link sent" card (anti-enumeration)
  note over E: sendPasswordResetEmail via AuthGateway → supabase.auth.resetPasswordForEmail -<br/>user completes reset from the emailed link
